metadata.name: Cheesus
metadata.description: Our Rodent, who art in the sewers, long be thy tail; thy basement come; thy will be done on earth as it is in the garbage can. Give us this day our daily cheese; and forgive us our squeakers as we forgive those who squeak against us; and lead us not into the mouse trap, but deliver us from poison. Amouse. Hail, Mice!
